{"tid":2215456,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁家傑斥封殺非主流媒體違憲","createTime":"2020-09-24T04:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T04:19:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95331cb2b11301b76be3503e200e469aae8684ef","tid":2215456,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/TGL6XU3EQVCGJPCCE7THVWSL3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FTGL6XU3EQVCGJPCCE7THVWSL3Y%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFB21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=d5de70de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FTGL6XU3EQVCGJPCCE7THVWSL3Y%2F&h=e738f3ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/TGL6XU3EQVCGJPCCE7THVWSL3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑斥封殺非主流媒體違憲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yOfA6ZNSZCz_VLGmkcAfm6NJQeg=/881x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TH4XRTB76JGXDLVE3JQZLSL63M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyOfA6ZNSZCz_VLGmkcAfm6NJQeg%3D%2F881x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTH4XRTB76JGXDLVE3JQZLSL63M.jpg&h=358687b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁家傑<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方單方面宣佈收緊「傳媒代表」的定義，日後網媒、學生記者採訪，極可能受到警方無理阻撓甚至拘捕。香港記者協會透露會研究法律行動跟進，有法律界認為，《基本法》保障港人享有言論及新聞自由，指警方做法嚴重損害新聞自由，認為不論記者組織、傳媒工作者以至市民，都有理據就警方無理做法提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：郭嘉銓稱方便工作 楊健興：唔阻攝錄當幫忙  警篩選傳媒 記協擬覆核<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警可照常執法 不應剝奪採訪權<br />\n<br />\n資深大律師梁家傑指出，港人的新聞自由受到《基本法》第27條涉及言論及新聞自由條文、《基本法》第39條訂明的《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》第19條和《香港人權法案》保障，認為記協有法律理據提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n梁斥警方收窄記者採訪自由的做法明顯不合乎比例，。。。。。。。。。。，其實都係違反咗保障新聞採訪自由嗰個重要憲制保障」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鬼祟改警例 「不影響行動」才配合採訪<br />\n<br />\n大律師兼法政滙思前召集人吳宗巒也指，。。。。。。。。。。，市民已非昔日般只靠主流傳媒獲取資訊。<br />\n<br />\n吳認為記協應盡快去信警方，。。。。。。。。。，同樣有法律基礎提出司法覆核。"},{"pid":"3691e2acc3a7549ece36e03bce068ff36ae8902c","tid":2215456,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"違憲 但係法治未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b547e644c2223f02feb7e6183e05989a5e00a9a0","tid":2215456,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"同佢地講無用<br />\n搞全球聯署，美國聯署<br />\n狂推Twitter戰線"}]}